    • Method Detail

      • load

        void load(ISingleModeTableModel model,
        boolean start_panel,
        boolean wait)
        Loads the data and sets them into the model.
        Parameters:
        model - the model
        start_panel - true if the function call is done from the start panel, false otherwise.
        If start_panel is true extra responsibilities are added based on the permission Permission.P_SB_MAILS_SEARCH_PROCESS. It lets to get more data for the mail inbox.
        wait - true if the wait cursor is to shown, false otherwise
